            . I live in Buckingham-street, Strand, and am a constable. On the morning of the 22nd of August I saw the prisoner and another lad in <placeName id="t18310908-100-crimeloc557">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-100-crimeloc557" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
